query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_conversations, 
       SUM(CASE WHEN userId != 2580001 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as real_conversations,
       SUM(CASE WHEN userId = 2580001 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as test_conversations
FROM conversations
LIMIT 1;
